<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> <unclear>sa</unclear>rvvadā tasya śrīmukha
<lb n="2" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> bhitilakassaujanyatējōṁkurassatyatyāgavarākramaikavasatissaubhāgyavidyādharaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> Abhyudyanmalayōdayādarinṛpadhvāṁtaṁ samuccā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭayan padmābhyunnatimunnayan pratidinaṁ dōrmmaṇḍalāgraśriyā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sa<unclear>dva</unclear>rggaṁ varipālayasvasuśatairāśāssadā pūrayan śūrō vaṁśakaraḥ kṣitau malayamā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>rttaṇḍaściraṁ rājatē [<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] sōyannirmmalakīrtti<unclear>varṇni</unclear>tajagaccālukyanārāyaṇaśrīrājyaikadhurandharaḥ kṛtamatissaṁkrāṁtikālōtsavē<supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>dākṣārāmanivāsinē bha
<lb n="5" break="no"/>gavatē bhīmēśvarādarāyādācaṁdrārkkamakhaṇḍavartti kṛtavān dīpaṁ jagaddīpakaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] sakavarṣa 1051 svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sarvvalōkāśraya śrīviṣṇuvarddhanamahārāju<unclear>lapra</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>varddhamāna vijayarājyasaṁvatsa 4 śrāhi veṁggināṇṭi malayamaṇḍalamuna cālukyasamuddharu<unclear>ṇḍe</unclear>na sūraparāju śrībhīmēsvaramahādēvaraku nuttarāya
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>na</unclear>saṁkrāṁtti nimittamunaṁ beṭṭina Akhaṇḍavartti lōhadaṇḍu diviya 1 ṇḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīniki dēvara kilaramuna nāvabōla prōlayayu gāṭabōla paṇḍayayu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
